{
  "texts": [
    "Data augmentation includes a set of techniques that change the size and quality of training datasets for an effective deep learning model.",
    "All these data augmentation techniques have been chosen by considering factors such as different positions, angles and light of hand movements during a possible conversation.",
    "The most important feature of data augmentation technique is that each image is used once during the training which reduces the training time of the network.",
    "In addition, the images in the dataset are randomly selected, which improves the predictive ability of the object detection network.",
    "Fig. 1010 Fig."
  ]
}